                This course has a bursary of £25,000 available to eligible trainees.
              </p>
              <p class="govuk-body">
                <a href="https://getintoteaching.education.gov.uk/funding-and-support/scholarships-and-bursaries">
                  Find out whether you are eligible for a bursary</a>.
              </p>
              <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">
                Student loans
              </h4>
              <p class="govuk-body">
                You may be eligible for student loans to cover the cost of your tuition fee or to help with living costs.
              </p>
              <p class="govuk-body">
                <a href="https://getintoteaching.education.gov.uk/funding-and-support/tuition-fee-and-maintenance-loans">
                  Find out more about student loans for teacher training</a>.
              </p>
            </div>
